Provide cultural sensitivity training for travel agents, tour guides, and hospitality staff to ensure that they understand and respect the cultural heritage of the destinations they visit. This training can include workshops, online courses, and certifications.

\subsection{Support Local Communities}
Encourage travelers to engage with local communities and support their efforts to preserve and share their cultural heritage. This can be done through responsible tourism initiatives, such as visiting local artisans, participating in cultural events, and purchasing locally-made products.

\subsection{Preservation of Cultural Sites}
